Digital India program of Government is a great initiative to transform India into a digitally empowered society and a knowledge based economy. Digital innovations are playing important role in knowledge sharing, research and capacity building in all sectors. These digital mediums will help us to make education and research more inclusive. Resilient Foundation for Academic Innovation &amp; Scientific being a non-profit organization is striving to be the contributor in Indias Global presence in academia, industry and scientific research. For this purpose, Foundation is providing a platform for collaboration of world reputed national &amp; international academic &amp; research organization including Industry. Such collaborations will help stakeholders to enhance their academic knowledge, skill and research ability.

